Subject: [PATCHv4 11/14] x86/mm: Make e820_end_ram_pfn() cover E820_TYPE_ACPI ranges
Date:   Tue,  5 Dec 2023 03:45:07 +0300
Message-ID: <20231205004510.27164-12-kirill.shutemov@linux.intel.com>
